- * Making love with you... *

54:25.265 --> 54:28.518
- I...

54:28.560 --> 54:30.395
I have to get back.

54:31.479 --> 54:33.565
Don't follow me.

54:33.606 --> 54:36.735
- * What more could I ask? *

54:36.776 --> 54:38.445
* There's nothing... *

54:38.486 --> 54:41.448
- Bob does not
really appreciate

54:41.489 --> 54:45.118
